"Os mû°dulos :mod:`collections` e :mod:`array` fornecem exemplos adicionais de "
"tipos de sequûˆncia mutûÀveis."

#: ../../reference/datamodel.rst:402
msgid "There are currently two intrinsic mutable sequence types:"
