"Como os argumentos sûÈo montados depende de ``a``:"

#: ../../reference/datamodel.rst:2126
msgid "Direct Call"
msgstr "Chamada direta"

#: ../../reference/datamodel.rst:2125
msgid ""
"The simplest and least common call is when user code directly invokes a "
