"retorna ``B.__dict__['x'].__get__(a, A)``. Se nûÈo for um descritor, ``x`` ûˋ "
"retornado inalterado."

#: ../../reference/datamodel.rst:2174
msgid ""
"For instance bindings, the precedence of descriptor invocation depends on "
